@startuml
title Activity Diagram: UC-10 Manage Local Inventory

|Manager|
start
:Navigate to 'Inventory Management';

|System|
:Display current stock levels;

|Manager|
:Perform manual physical stock count;
if (Physical Count == System Count?) then ([Yes])
  :Approve current count;
else ([No])
  :Enter stock adjustment into system;
  |System|
  :Prompt for adjustment reason;
  |Manager|
  :Log adjustment reason (e.g. Spoilage);
endif

|System|
:Save updated inventory records;
:Log timestamp and manager ID;
stop
@enduml
